title: LOOKING FOR ROOMIES FOR 3 BED 3 BATH HOUSE
posting_body: ['*READ BEFORE MESSAGING*', '**SERIOUS INQUIRES ONLY**', 'Looking for new CLEAN, QUIET and RESPONSIBLE housemates for this two-story beautiful house.', 'Current housemates are leaving in august or september when the lease ends!', 'I will need to sign a new lease, for another year.', 'A little about me:', 'I work at In n out, planning on getting a second job', 'so I’ll be busy.', 'I have a 3 year old dog, she’s sweet, quiet and friendly, half chihuahua/rottweiler.', 'About the place:', 'I have three bedrooms freeing up august or September for $1100 each all of which are unfurnished.', 'I will need proof of income.', 'This does not include utilities which are another $50-70 a month.', 'I will need a deposit of 500 before you move in.', 'Couples/roommates are welcomed to share the room if you’d like.', 'You’ll be sharing the bathroom with two other roommates.', 'There’s an in unit washer and dryer.', 'Location:', 'Great location, it’s located by high school, Target, Evergreen, Costco business center ect.', 'I can’t really show off the rooms since the housemates are still living here and because of privacy.', 'But I can show u the house, the kitchen and living room and backyard so we could meet in person.', 'There’s plenty of street parking.', 'If i am not able to find housemates by augusr or September 1st will be moving out.', 'If you see this post up this is still available.', 'Thank you!', 'Message me for more info and an introduction of yourself!']
